          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">SKIP</td><td class="pr-4 font-mono text-sm">{'{P}'} skip {'{P}'}</td><td>Doing nothing preserves anything</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">COMP</td><td class="pr-4 font-mono text-sm">{'{P}'}c₁{'{R}'}, {'{R}'}c₂{'{Q}'} ⇒ {'{P}'}c₁;c₂{'{Q}'}</td><td>Chain postconditions. <strong>The handshake.</strong></td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">WHILE</td><td class="pr-4 font-mono text-sm">{'{b∧P}'} c {'{P}'} ⇒ {'{P}'} while b do c {'{P∧¬b}'}</td><td>Loop invariant survives</td></tr>
